 Destructor turned as the fire came at him. He dodged it. HE TURNED TO 
mAGNUS.."gAIN SOME ORDER HERE!"
MAGNUS FLOATED UPWARDS... a light shined from the oracal. The voice of the 
oracal came out..."Everyone stop fighting. NOW!!!"
(All my chars there stand and watch.)
